			<node ID="ID_304763095" TEXT="Server-Side Code. There are several server-side technologies that can be used when developing web applications. The most popular is Microsoft&#8217;s ASP.NET. In ASP.NET server-side code uses the .NET Framework and is written in languages like C# and VB.NET. Server-side processing is used to interact with permanent storage like databases or files." />
